{"tid":2233323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：每日跟蹤黃之鋒鄒家成車輛登記人 都與兩名警務人員同名同姓火","createTime":"2020-10-07T04:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T05:26:52.000Z","uid":22556,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e34719afc16a68999986792b101b999fdaccdb11","tid":2233323,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"國安法實施後不同政界人士都被不明人士跟蹤，前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒更發現被長期監視，黃之鋒昨披露，與協助12港人家屬的本土派鄒家成疑遭同一車隊跟蹤。本報根據黃之鋒提及的兩輛私家車登記資料，發現登記車主與兩名警務人員同名同姓。黃之鋒表明，即使政權每天監視製造白色恐怖，也不會拖垮他的意志。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者昨晚按地址分別到曉麗苑向女車主求證事件，當記者透過大廈對講機與單位內人士對話，一名女子接聽，確認姓岑女車主當時在單位內，該名女子查問記者所為何事，但當記者表明身份，希望轉告岑女，對方即關掉對講機。另外，記者去到粉嶺名都單位按動大廈對講機，但無人發聲，並直接中斷對講機，無法接觸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/OOV4KWK5E5GTTIZZUCJAFVQGYQ/?fbclid=IwAR11Y5OJPerjaMV08rX5H3z9ttxlI45rtpNajWBTeK1dQRsSgcOOV_pvIuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FOOV4KWK5E5GTTIZZUCJAFVQGYQ%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR11Y5OJPerjaMV08rX5H3z9ttxlI45rtpNajWBTeK1dQRsSgcOOV_pvIuY&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=d13dfb37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FOOV4KWK5E5GTTIZZUCJAFVQGYQ%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR11Y5OJPerjaMV08rX5H3z9ttxlI45rtpNajWBTeK1dQRsSgcOOV_pvIuY&h=c0c7d49b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/OOV4KWK5E5GTTIZZUCJAFVQGYQ/?fbclid=IwAR11Y5OJPerjaMV08rX5H3z9ttxlI45rtpNajWBTeK1dQRsSgcOOV_pvIuY</a>"},{"pid":"bb6e3689c0db097487f365b52ecc61dc5ac888ab","tid":2233323,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f43c6ec98ab320bb143b9bcd0f08428d22c83bcd","tid":2233323,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pi